NANO Editior
NANO Editor 

sreekanth@dell:~$ nano --version
 GNU nano, version 4.8

nano filename
nano -v filename                  to view file in Read only mode

ctrl + v         to go to bottom
ctrl + o         to saveas
ctrl + x         save changes Yes or NO
ctrl + w        to search for a word
ctrl + \          to replace the word
ctrl + k         to cut the text
ctrl + u         paste the text




Enable password authentication
nano /etc/ssh/sshd_config
Ctrl + w  -- to search window
search for passwordauthen
make changes to yes
ctrtl + x save
service sshd restart

replace a keyword
ctrl + \  replace the word

cut the text
ctrl + k to cut the text

copy the text
alt+6

paste the text
ctrl + u
